  "name": "Pegasos Deluxe Beach Hotel",
  "description": "The cosmopolitan Pegasos Deluxe Beach Hotel welcomes you to its facilities and promise you the most enjoyable vacation in Rhodes Island. Located right on the beach just a few minutes away from famous monument of Kallithea Springs and 10 minutes from UNESCO World Heritage \"Medieval Rhodes Town\" . Pegasos Deluxe Beach Hotel is a spectacular resort located on the East Coast of Rhodes, 2 km away from the centre of Faliraki. Steps away from sandy beach and crystal water and the unique seafront location of the hotel with the dramatic backdrop of the green mountains and lush gardens gives you the sensation of being in another world full of contrasts. Our Hotel is ideal for family vacations, romantic holidays, weddings in our St. George chapel, honeymoons, professional meetings & seminars. We offer 397 elegant guest rooms & suites with Free Wi-Fi. Hotel serves a fabulous concept for unique gourmet experience in our “Elia” A la Carte Restaurant.",
